Question: Both images show exteriors, and the left image shows a primitive yurt-type structure with no windows and with gray material around it, while the right shows a structure with a black cap on its peak.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://besidethehedgerow.files.wordpress.com/2015/03/dsc_0040.jpg

Right image URL: https://svargaonearth.files.wordpress.com/2015/10/img_3901.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the image an exterior?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the image an exterior?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image show a primitive yurt-type structure with no windows and with gray material around it?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image show a structure with a black cap on its peak?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} and {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
